## This file contains the ideas for this specific project
This project will implement a rust program that uses the ffmpeg library to create a comprehensive media conversion library.

It will need a Web API interface, a cli, a MCP server and a plugin for the tts hub on alexandria.

Do your research and design a thorough plan. Do not execute until explicit approval in given and this project is restricted to teh video-convertor-rs folder for writing but you can read the alexandria dir tree for designing if you need.

Please ask questions after analysis before finalizing your plan. You will need to research the ffmpeg codec webpage to make this work well.
